The controls are fine & everything ran smoothly, no glitches. As for the story, I could see the ending coming a mile off. It's very smart to have the episodes separate, the first for free & the others fairly low in price. There's no way I would have paid over ¬£5 for this otherwise.

replyContent: Hi Helen, the answer to your question is simple, Google Play store max game size is 150MB, our game was 440MB if combined. If we would exceed the size, I would need to add server and have costs that we cant have at the moment. Once google increases the supported app size, we might think about merging it.
